watchdog: bcm2835_wdt: Fix module autoload

The commit 5e6acc3e678e ("bcm2835-pm: Move bcm2835-watchdog's DT probe
to an MFD.") broke module autoloading on Raspberry Pi. So add a
module alias this fix this.

